# EXAMPLE.md — How to Add Sections to This App

This file shows concrete, copy-paste examples for extending the app with new sections and state.

---

## Example 1: Minimal Static Section

The simplest possible section — no props, no state, just content.

**`src/components/sections/HelloSection.tsx`**
```tsx
export default function HelloSection() {
  return (
    <section className="section-card hello-section">
